text: Princeton is a Canadian district municipality in British Columbia, Canada. Princeton is in the Similkameen region of British Columbia. The population of Princeton as of 2021 is 2,894. The current mayor of Princeton is Spencer Coyne. Princeton is also known for it's castle, which is on the outskirts of Princeton. The castle is now a resort. ==Other websites== *City of Princeton's Official website Category:Cities in British Columbia
title: Princeton, British Columbia
